KitKat::

She heard Perceptor and logic overcame her current frame of mind. She 
stood down and reholstered her plasmapistol. Nods towards 
Perceptor. "He's right. Wait here untill Hyrdas comes."
SHe turned and looked at SharpClaw. "Keep an eye on her. I will be 
right back."

She went off towards the med bay.


Battera::
She watched as the femme bot left and refolded her wings around her 
shoulders. "Well, at least some bots have sence. I try to join the 
most power group of warriors, and I almost become scrap. I just want 
to get back at those who imprisoned me. I do not wish to fight with 
the one's I'm trying to join with."

She sighed and put a delicate hand on her small hip.
